data.description: Welcome to Lakeland Village! This charming home offers 3 bedrooms w/ a 4th bedroom downstairs perfect for hosting all of your guests. Fresh paint and a new kitchen with SS appliances create a bright and inviting atmosphere. Outside enjoy a detached shop and just under half acre of space providing plenty of room for activities. Located just off the Lakeland Village golf course and a minute walk to the clubhouse, The Bistro restaurant, between Lake Anderson and North Bay, this home provides endless possibilities for outdoor activities and relaxation. Don't miss out on this idyllic Lakeland Village gem! Newer roof, deck, and furnace. 2 car garage +RV parking, fully fenced. There are incredible opportunities to make your home dreams come true!
